  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b8e\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf-\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd-\u0b87\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1-\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bbe/175-300941",
  "time_ut": 1658505053,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bbe ?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Do you understand our resolution now?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Those who criticized us will now understand that we did not elect Ranil Wickremesinghe and that our decision to prevent his victory was correct. Tamil National Federation media spokesperson and Member of Parliament MA Sumanthran said that Ranil has demonstrated his power after taking office.",
        "While it was announced to field United National Party leader Ranil Wickremesinghe as the presidential candidate of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, the Tamil National Federation rejected it and decided to support the other candidate, Dallas Alagaperuma.",
        "Although there were two different positions within the TNA, severe criticism was leveled at the TNA regarding the party's decision.",
        "In this case, on the same night that President Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in, the demonstrators were attacked. Sumandran MP said the above while commenting on those attacks.",
        "The protestors' democratic struggle was justified, and they would have gone peacefully yesterday if they had announced that they would return and leave the seized government property. But it was never acceptable that the security forces launched such a brutal attack on them in the middle of the night. We strongly condemn this.",
        "From the very beginning we insisted on forming an all-party government. Our stand is that the solution to the crisis is to form a national government that includes the main opposition party, the independent party, the Tamil National Federation and other Tamil Muslim parties. But on the other hand Ranil Wickremesinghe was simply a budding party candidate.",
        "Today the party has become a party rejected by the people. People have taken a stand that not only their President, Prime Minister but also none of the Rajapaks can be in the Cabinet.",
        "In that case majority in Parliament is not a mandate of the people. So we took the right decision. Within 24 hours of taking over the executive power, Ranil had revealed his true nature. So the reason for not supporting him is soon revealed."
      ],
